(328, 'El perro perdido', 'Rosa María Rey, Andrés Martínez Ricci', 'Editorial desconocida', '9789507531590', '2005', 'One day Nicolás and his dog, Orfio, go to the park to play with friends. When Orfio wanders off and Nicolás can\'t find him, Nicolás wonders if he will ever see his friend again. Presented in comic book format.', 'Infantiles', 1, 1, 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=m5-SAAAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api'),
